					.info__present-content
						p.info__subtitle
							span
								|Protect yourself
							|and make sure you are not selling someone's patented invention.

						.info__cards-wrap
							.info__card
								p.info__title-card
									|Sylicon wine cap
								img.info__pic-card(src="/static/images/content/card-1.png", alt="the image is missing")
								p.info__subtitle-card
									|Active patent <br> High  risk to sell

							.info__card
								p.info__title-card
									|Shower head <br> with mineral filler
								img.info__pic-card(src="/static/images/content/card-2.png", alt="the image is missing")
								p.info__subtitle-card.info__subtitle-card_active
									|Expired patent <br> Totally safe to sell

							.info__card
								p.info__title-card
									|Full Face <br> Snorkel Mask
								img.info__pic-card(src="/static/images/content/card-3.png", alt="the image is missing")
								p.info__subtitle-card
									|Active patent <br> High  risk to sell



